name: Variable Term Agreement
title: VTA
definition: Identifies the duration identifying USOC contract date or contract identification number of any variable term agreement that may be offered by a provider.
fieldNotes: When the ASC-EC field is populated this identifies   the duration identifying USOC contract date or   contract identification number of any variable term   agreement that may be offered by ASC-EC.
exampleNotes: This example illustrates a numeric value but is left   justified since it is treated as text.    V TPPP   0 82089
